#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _posts/2026-05-01-quarkus-3-35-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus 3.35 - JAR tree-shaking, PGO for native, Semeru AOT, @Transactional for Hibernate Reactive, and more"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.35 - JAR tree-shaking, PGO para nativos, Semeru AOT, @Transactional para Hibernate Reactive, y más"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#: _posts/2026-05-01-quarkus-3-35-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We released Quarkus 3.35, which comes with JAR tree-shaking, Profile-Guided Optimization for native builds, Semeru AOT support, @Transactional support for Hibernate Reactive, and several other improvements."
msgstr "Hemos lanzado Quarkus 3.35, que viene con JAR tree-shaking, Profile-Guided Optimization para construcciones nativas, soporte Semeru AOT, soporte @Transactional para Hibernate Reactive, y varias otras mejoras."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-01-quarkus-3-35-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We're pleased to announce the release of Quarkus 3.35."
msgstr "Nos complace anunciar el lanzamiento de Quarkus 3.35."

