#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-01-quarkus-3-35-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/53339[#53339] - Semeru AOT support"
msgstr "link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/53339[#53339] - Soporte para Semeru AOT"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-01-quarkus-3-35-released.adoc
